Class OrderingCoffeeController

java.lang.Object
application.OrderingCoffeeController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class OrderingCoffeeController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class is a Controller for the Coffee menu. It allows users to add Coffee to their order.
Author:
Kiernan King and Ahmed Alghazwi
